abstract: Minnesota Lynx defeat Atlanta Dream, 88-74, to lead WNBA finals, 1-0.
snippet: Rebekkah Brunson had 26 points and 11 rebounds and Seimone Augustus added 22 points to lead the Lynx to an 88-74 victory over the Dream in Game 1 of the W.N.B.A. finals.
lead_paragraph: Rebekkah Brunson had 26 points and 11 rebounds and Seimone Augustus added 22 points to lead the Lynx to an 88-74 victory over the Dream in Game 1 of the W.N.B.A. finals.

headline.seo: W.N.B.A. Finals: Minnesota Rallies Past Atlanta
